WEBVTT

00:02.001 --> 00:03.379
Previously on "The Originals"...

00:03.380 --> 00:05.976
I assume I have the misfortune
of speaking to my mother.

00:05.977 --> 00:07.616
I have come to heal our family.

00:07.617 --> 00:10.038
I will undo everything
that has been done,

00:10.039 --> 00:12.200
thereby giving you a new life.

00:12.201 --> 00:15.013
Well, I'd prefer you both to
join me against our mother,

00:15.014 --> 00:16.996
but I'll happily settle
for one or the other.

00:16.997 --> 00:19.113
I will not stop
until every single vampire

00:19.114 --> 00:21.233
in New Orleans has
ceased to exist,

00:21.234 --> 00:23.507
and I will show
no mercy to anyone

00:23.508 --> 00:24.956
who dares stand with them.

00:24.957 --> 00:26.992
My wolves...
I think I figured out

00:26.993 --> 00:29.233
a way to release them
from the witches.

00:29.937 --> 00:32.164
I have to marry Jackson.

00:34.734 --> 00:35.892
Rebekah: Hello, mother.

00:35.893 --> 00:37.261
I believe you're
offering a deal.

00:37.262 --> 00:38.965
Your beautiful soul will live on

00:38.966 --> 00:40.535
in the body of another.

00:42.575 --> 00:44.534
You must be feeling
a little twitchy.

00:44.535 --> 00:46.351
That's what happens
when you're in transition.

00:46.967 --> 00:48.541
I couldn't stop the spell.

00:48.542 --> 00:50.302
Davina: You swear she's safe?

00:50.303 --> 00:51.260
Perfectly.

00:51.261 --> 00:52.481
[Gasps]

00:55.015 --> 00:57.094
I'm Rebekah Mikaelson!

01:00.564 --> 01:02.497
Hi, honey.
Mama's here.

01:02.498 --> 01:04.069
Ohh.

01:04.071 --> 01:06.140
Klaus, voice-over: It has been
said that all love begins

01:06.141 --> 01:10.050
and ends with she
who gave us life.

01:10.051 --> 01:12.124
A thousand years ago,
my mother turned us

01:12.125 --> 01:13.925
into monsters,

01:13.926 --> 01:17.330
yet still she claimed
to love her children,

01:17.331 --> 01:20.200
even as she vowed to destroy us.

01:24.479 --> 01:26.785
The noble Elijah,

01:26.786 --> 01:31.193
tormented by long buried,
shameful secrets.

01:31.194 --> 01:32.307
Aah! Aah!

01:36.734 --> 01:38.396
[Shudders]

01:40.973 --> 01:43.795
Kol, the wily troublemaker...

01:46.514 --> 01:50.058
Out for no one but himself.

01:50.059 --> 01:52.534
Finn,

01:52.535 --> 01:54.573
the devoted acolyte,

01:54.574 --> 01:56.709
his love all too easily warped

01:56.710 --> 01:59.112
by our mother's sick hate.

02:03.489 --> 02:06.144
Fierce Rebekah,

02:06.145 --> 02:07.904
willing to risk everything
on the chance

02:07.905 --> 02:12.479
that she might one day
find happiness,

02:12.480 --> 02:16.655
and me, the bastard child,

02:16.656 --> 02:19.559
my mother's greatest shame.

02:19.560 --> 02:22.274
Now finally, we have
defeated her,

02:22.732 --> 02:27.075
giving her the choice
she never thought to give us,

02:27.076 --> 02:32.588
to live on as one
of the monsters she created

02:32.589 --> 02:34.958
or suffer the slow,
agonizing death

02:34.959 --> 02:36.930
she so deserves.

02:36.931 --> 02:38.760
Um, congratulations, I guess,

02:38.761 --> 02:42.275
but right now,
I'm a little more worried about Finn,

02:42.276 --> 02:44.599
considering I totally
stabbed him in the back.

02:44.600 --> 02:46.082
He won't find you here.

02:46.083 --> 02:49.356
This is the safest place
you could possibly be.

02:49.357 --> 02:52.137
Come on. There's someone
I want you to meet.

02:56.292 --> 02:57.706
I'd like to introduce you

02:57.707 --> 03:00.611
to the newest member
of our family,

03:00.612 --> 03:03.750
the little troublemaker all
the fuss has been about.

03:03.751 --> 03:04.853
Camille...

03:04.854 --> 03:06.121
[Door opens]

03:06.122 --> 03:08.394
This is hope.

03:09.899 --> 03:12.202
Oh, my God.

03:12.203 --> 03:15.130
What? You said...
I thought she was...

03:15.131 --> 03:16.603
The only way
to truly protect her

03:16.604 --> 03:18.705
was to convince
the world of her death.

03:21.143 --> 03:23.380
I hope you understand

03:23.381 --> 03:24.715
once it's safe
for you to leave here,

03:24.716 --> 03:27.422
our secret cannot
leave with you.

